stories.title: West Indies v Australia, Sixth One-day Inernational
Hinds leads Windies to glory
stories.summary: When Australia's unprecedented run of 21 consecutive victories finally came to an end at Port-of-Spain last week, Ricky Ponting had described the result as a wake-up call for his side
